The paper also presents a uniform inverse preservation of recognizability result, which is a topic that falls under the category of formal languages and automata theory. Therefore, cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also a likely category. 

The paper also deals with encoding pushdown systems into trees, which is a topic that falls under the category of data structures and algorithms. Therefore, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a likely category.
